data.description: Same owner since 1997! This one owner home beams with pride of ownership. Roof 2017, AC 2019, Water Heater 2010, and newer flooring in most areas. Accordion storm shutters will make hurricane preparation quick and easy. Enjoy the large screened back porch and spacious quarter acre lot with matching detached shed for extra storage. Practical floor plan with split bedroom concept and walk-in closet space. This charming home has so much to offer. Come and see for yourself!
